ğŸš€ Installation

Clone the repository:

git clone https://github.com/iosdevashu177singh/movieapp.git

Navigate to the project directory:

cd movieapp

Install dependencies using CocoaPods:

pod install

Open the .xcworkspace file:

open MovieApp.xcworkspace

Build and run the project in Xcode.

ğŸ“¡ API Integration

This app fetches data from The Movie Database (TMDB) API.
Make sure to add your API Key in APIService.swift:

private let apiKey = "9a7243213d79e4344f8f16ce3b6098cf"
you can use your own.

